code: @Override public boolean canBuild(FormattingOptions formattingOptions) {     return super.canBuild(formattingOptions) && ObjectHelper.isNotEmpty(formattingOptions.getPattern()). }
@Override public Format<?> build(FormattingOptions formattingOptions) {     return new DoublePatternFormat(formattingOptions.getPattern(), formattingOptions.getLocale()). }

@Override public Double parse(String string) throws Exception {     if (getNumberFormat() != null) {         return getNumberFormat().parse(string).doubleValue().     } else {         return Double.valueOf(string).     } }
